{
  "stem": "22944.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in our town, in Bratislava, that area, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] people start walking with all swastikas-- youngsters-- all the disrupting people, in a sense that they came to disrupt us in a Synagogue service just to make commotions.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] people used to disappear.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This I do remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father used to come home and tell us that so and so disappeared.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We do not know where he or she is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some attractive women were disappearing, so they were afraid that they took them to do unpleasant work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] shouting, throwing stones.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Generally, it was bit of a fear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we sort of huddled together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All the Jewish people knew each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it's a kind of feeling insecurity.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Actually, I do remember, as a five, six year old, certain amount of insecurity, people sort of not knowing where to do, where to go, so on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I do remember this bit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did feel the fear, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, one day, my-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was it New Year, or it was Rosh Hashanah, or it was Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't tell exactly, but there was a commotion coming one day that there is a lorry of Slovakian soldiers arrived-- and middle of the service-- disrupting the service, and all of the shuls of the prayer people, and told them to go on a lorry.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were taken away, and it was a terrible commotion and-- because, obviously, they're very religious people in the first.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was very important to observe the festival.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was the beginning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I saw that on one occasion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I ran home to tell my mother about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I used to go out, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
